---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Books" description="Books about worldview, faith, meaning, and living on purpose.">

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-20">

    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-medium mb-14">Books</h1>

    <!-- Featured Book: WAB -->
    <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-8">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-3">Coming soon</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-medium mb-4">We All Believe</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Everyone operates from a worldview - a set of beliefs about reality, meaning, and
          how to live. Most people have never examined theirs. <em>We All Believe</em> is an
          invitation to do exactly that.
        </p>
        <p>
          Through the lens of the Five Forces - the five ways humans experience reality -
          this book helps readers understand not just what they believe, but why they believe it,
          and what that means for how they live.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

</BaseLayout>
